--- Changes ---
1. NEW:  backend/migrations/120_password_reset_tokens.up.sql
   - password_reset_tokens table: id, user_id, token, expires_at, consumed, created_at
   - Indexes on token (UNIQUE) and user_id

2. NEW:  backend/migrations/120_password_reset_tokens.down.sql
   - DROP TABLE IF EXISTS password_reset_tokens

3. NEW:  backend/internal/repository/password_reset_repo.go
   - PasswordResetToken struct
   - GenerateToken() — 32 bytes crypto/rand → base64 URL-encoded
   - CreateResetToken(ctx, userID) — store token with 24h expiry
   - ValidateResetToken(ctx, token) — check not consumed, not expired
   - ConsumeResetToken(ctx, token) — mark consumed after use
   - HashPassword(password) — delegates to pkg/hash argon2id

4. MOD:  backend/internal/connect/admin/admin_user_handler.go
   - AdminUserServer struct: added resetRepo *repository.PasswordResetRepo
   - NewAdminUserServer signature: +resetRepo param
   - ResetUserPassword: no longer returns plaintext
     · Generate random token as temp password
     · Hash via repository.HashPassword (argon2id)
     · Store hash in DB via AdminRepository.ResetUserPassword
     · Create one-time reset token for self-service
     · Response: {NewPassword: ""} — empty, not plaintext

5. MOD:  backend/cmd/server/main.go
   - L340: passwordResetRepo := repository.NewPasswordResetRepo(pool)
   - L349: NewAdminUserServer(adminRepo, passwordResetRepo, log)

